title: Hour 1 - Deshaun Watson Settles, Daniel Snyder in Trouble, Mike Florio
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Deshaun Watson Settles, Daniel Snyder in Trouble, Mike Florio
description:
Dan discusses Deshaun Watson's sudden settlement with most (but not all) of his accusers, tackles the mess that Washington Commanders owner Daniel Snyder finds himself in, and he chats with Mike Florio about all of it.
